author: Stilgherrian
title: My Health Record woes detailed in leaked document: Report
description: It's time for the Australian Digital Health Agency to take a strategic approach, but it seems it would rather fix problems 'on the fly' or just ignore them.
content: A leaked document from the agency responsible for Australia's centralised digital health records reveals an organisation that's still on the defensive. In some cases it's even still in denial about problems with the system. The document, obtained by Healthcarâ€¦ [+6430 chars]
